uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.proxystore

Class ProxyStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.Store
      • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.proxystore.ProxyStore

  • public class ProxyStore
extends Store
    Gaffer ProxyStore implementation.

    The ProxyStore is simply a Gaffer store which delegates all operations to a Gaffer REST API.
